title: Catoctin Mountain Park: Headquarters
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Places To Go     Headquarters              Headquarters          Â     Headquarters, sometimes called Peniel, is the administrative center for the park. The visitor center is located one mile west on Route 77. Stop by there for maps and general information or call (301) 663-9388.For information about permits or contracting, please call Headquarters staff at (301) 663-9330. Directions to Headquarters.
